i18n.longDescription:
You've got the Sim, you've got the house, you've got the job, now it’s time to add a swanky new car with The Sims 3: Fast Lane Stuff for the PC.

Choose the car you've always wanted and watch it change your Sims’ lives. There are four styles of vehicle: Racing, Intrigue, Rockabilly, and Classic Luxury. Each car comes with its own furnishing and apparel options, so you can pimp your ride.

As you drive your new car (or cars), you’ll decorate your home to match the feel of your new automobile. After all, a luxury car calls for an upscale lifestyle full of champagne and chandeliers, so if you live in a small, humble home, you’ll need a serious style upgrade to complement your fancy car.

This new pack allows you to customize your car, home, and Sim to reflect your status. Are you wealthy? Are you a speed demon who likes to rev the engine and drift around the corner? Perhaps you live a life of mystery, driving sleek black cars with tinted windows. Or maybe you’re a tough guy with sunglasses and greasy hair, a rebel without any of those pesky causes.

With this pack you’ll obtain the car you’ve been drooling over and show it off to all of the other Sims on the block.

Features:
• Give your Sims the rides they’ve always dreamed of — and the lifestyles that go with them.
• Enjoy four all-new styles of fashions, furnishings, and vehicles: Racing, Intrigue, Rockabilly, and Classic Luxury.
• Create the ultimate garage to house your Sim’s professional race car or hot rod.
• Deck out your Sim’s house in luxurious accessories to match their sleek new, luxurious rides.
i18n.onlineDisclaimer: REQUIRES THE SIMS 3 GAME ON PC (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES TO PLAY.
